ragraph","text":"4． 1954年杀掉462名。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"fe30b60479","type":"paragraph","text":"投入劳改的反革命犯累计6797名。截至今年2月底，现押反革命犯共7529名，其中有外地临时寄押的15名；投入劳改的有6611名，次数中包括一部分由华北，天津移交过来的。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"8856d217dc","type":"paragraph","text":"对刑事犯的打击 … 自1951年至 1954年底共逮捕刑事犯罪分子24708名。其中：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"e811993e65","type":"paragraph","text":"1． 1951年逮捕8644名；","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"57efa3e703","type":"paragraph","text":"2． 1952年逮捕4429名；","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"192afbd3ae","type":"paragraph","text":"3． 1953年逮捕5806名；","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"828a50e863","type":"paragraph","text":"4． 1954年逮捕5829名。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"5eb62cd4c1","type":"paragraph","text":"其中一共杀掉84名，投入劳改累计14327名，至今年2月底现押 7862名，已投入劳改6567名。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"c052490f71","type":"appellation","text":"……","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"},{"id":"34d712b43c","type":"paragraph","text":"从现在掌握的各种材料分析，估计今年可捕反革命分子2千至2千5百名，刑事犯罪分子6千至6千5百名。…(pp. 27-9)","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2"}],"page":{"id":"e2155dadcf","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cff5b38c2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}